    <Constant name="CUBITS_ARABIC" id="dcc8f7c9-be2d-4154-a45a-693d69feaa47">
        <source>6</source>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>There are eight different identified cubits:

Arabic					1 cubit = 4.80 x 10^-1 metres
Greek, Attic			1 cubit = 6.171200 x 10^-1 metres
Hachemic, Arabic		1 cubit = 6.40 x 10^-1 metres
Hebrew					1 cubit = 0.555 metres
Hebrew, sacred system	1 cubit = 0.640 metres
new, Arabic				1 cubit = 4.80 x 10^-1 metres
Persian					1 cubit = 0.640 metres
Roman					1 cubit = 0.4416 metres
UK						1 cubit = 0.4572 metres</text>
    </Constant>
